### Actual Output:
@startuml input-output-hk_marlowe-starter-kit
left to right direction
skinparam rectangle {
  BackgroundColor #ffffff
  BorderColor black
  Style roundrect
}
skinparam defaultTextAlignment center

actor "Developer" as Dev
rectangle "Jupyter Notebooks" as Jupyter
rectangle "Marlowe CLI Tools" as CLI
rectangle "dApp UI" as UI
rectangle "Wallet (Nami/Eternl)" as Wallet

package "Marlowe Runtime" {
  rectangle "Proxy" as Proxy
  rectangle "Chain Indexer" as ChainIndexer
  rectangle "Chain Sync" as ChainSync
  rectangle "Contract" as Contract
  rectangle "Indexer" as Indexer
  rectangle "Sync" as Sync
  rectangle "Tx" as Tx
  rectangle "Web Server" as WebServer
}

database "PostgreSQL" as Postgres
cloud "Cardano Blockchain" as Cardano

Dev --> Jupyter : Learns/Executes
Dev --> CLI : Runs commands
Dev --> UI : Interacts

UI --> Wallet : CIP30/CIP45\nconnect/sign
Wallet --> Cardano : Submit tx

Jupyter --> WebServer : API calls
CLI --> WebServer : API calls
UI --> WebServer : API calls

Proxy --> ChainIndexer
Proxy --> ChainSync
Proxy --> Contract
Contract --> Indexer
Contract --> Sync
Contract --> Tx
WebServer --> Proxy

ChainIndexer --> Cardano : Queries
ChainSync --> Cardano : Syncs
Tx --> Cardano : Submits
Indexer --> Postgres : Stores
Sync --> Postgres : Stores

note right of WebServer
  REST API endpoints:
  - Contract management
  - Transaction construction
  - UTxO queries
end note
@enduml